<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
      <h1>You've been invited to join SSStutterBuddy!</h1>
      
      <p>Hi there,</p>
      
      <p><strong><%= @invited_by_name %></strong> has invited you to join SSStutterBuddy, a platform dedicated to advancing stuttering research by connecting researchers with people who stutter.</p>
      
      <p>SSStutterBuddy is a community where:</p>
      <ul style="margin: 20px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
        <li>People who stutter can discover and join relevant research opportunities</li>
        <li>Researchers can find participants for their studies</li>
        <li>We work together to advance our understanding of stuttering</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>To get started, simply click the button below to create your account:</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="<%= @signup_url %>" style="background-color: #2563EB; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold;">
          Join SSStutterBuddy
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>Signing up is free and takes just a few minutes.</strong></p>
      
      <p>If you have any questions about SSStutterBuddy, please read more about us on our <a href="https://ssstutterbuddy.com/faq">website</a>.</p>

      <p>If you are not interested in joining SSStutterBuddy, we apologize for the inconvenience and please ignore this email. We will not contact you again.</p>
      
      <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;" />
      
      <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
        Best regards,<br />
        The SSStutterBuddy Team<br />
        <a href="mailto:support@ssstutterbuddy.com">support@ssstutterbuddy.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html> 